Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OVA第一話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WATER·WAR！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一戰的賽場在南方的小島上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然開場說了一句“所以呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是到底是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定俗成的吐槽真像小桃桃的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我小桃桃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 難得有海灘 大家不如下水游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是個好點子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..沒有泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有學校指定的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家一起去買吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百貨公司裏面有很棒的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！大家一起去買泳衣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡是和泳衣沾邊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種各樣一應俱全就是這家店的賣點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從古至今？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無奇不有？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 所有種類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再現了龐貝壁畫的最古老的兩件式泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,19世紀的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜聞樂見的條紋泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古今東西的電影明星穿著的時尚名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連封面女郎穿著的泳裝也可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:02:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夢幻的吸睛泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人..穿這個會受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要亂講啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個看起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗶嗡~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是淑女們最愛的花紋泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這件是走少女風格的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魅力無法擋啊 果然要這樣才對嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥特風的泳衣 一直很想穿穿看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這款是帶有佩斯利花紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上這件我就是風韻熟女了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是比起這些..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得今年的主流會是戰車風哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是戰車！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳指的是豹紋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.46,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(705,660)}Panther
